title: Cannabis Collection - Weediquette - Stoned Kids Cure Cancer
description:
Today i have a new addition to the Cannabis Collection! For over four years i have been seeding my uploads in this Cannabis Collection and i managed to keep over 50 dvd's alive, so if you are interested in cannabis check out this collection on the Pirate Bay. I really need some serious seeding help with them, as most of them get a few downloads per week. So please don't hit and run but stay seeding for a while. Together we can keep the Cannabis Collection alive! Thanks to all the peers from all over the world helping to seed.

The Cannabis Collection - a series of educative and entertaining info dvd's

Please enjoy, share with friends and seed :)

Weediquette is a documentary series airing on Viceland that follows host, and Vice correspondent, Krishna Andavolu as he chronicles the science, culture and economics of the legalization of marijuana.

Episode 1 - Stoned Kids

Many families whose children have cancer are using medical marijuana in their cancer therapy.
